##Welcome to Treeverse
Treeverse is an open-world, fantasy MMORPG with a MOBA-style combat system. Slay beasts, forge mighty weapons, lure the biggest fish, form guilds, defeat dungeons and explore the deep lore. The living world of Treeverse awaits those bold enough to conquer it.

#What are Treeverse Founders' Land?
10420, Utility-based NFTs that allow holders to place in the game world and has the following benefits
- Public Homes
- Better Customizability
- Rent Them Out
- Teleport Destination
- Extra Storage Space

- Follow us on Twitter : [Twitter](https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse)
